@baseUrl = http://localhost:9090/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

### ========================================
### Bind 错误测试
### ========================================

### 0. Bind 错误 - JSON 格式不正确（缺少引号）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD00",
  "name": 测试公司,
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "张三",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "expired_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 2
}

### 0.1 Bind 错误 - 类型不匹配（type 传字符串）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD01",
  "name": "类型错误测试",
  "type": "不是数字",
  "contact_name": "张三",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "expired_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 2
}

### 0.2 Bind 错误 - JSON 语法错误（缺少大括号）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD02",
  "name": "语法错误测试",
  "type": 1
}

### ========================================
### 租户 API 测试
### ========================================

### 1. 创建租户 - 企业类型
# @name createTenantCompany
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD12",
  "name": "测试科技有限公司",
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "张三",
  "email": "zhangsan@test.com",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "expired_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 2
}

### 2. 创建租户 - 个人类型
# @name createTenantPersonal
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "110101199001011234",
  "name": "李四个体户",
  "type": 2,
  "contact_name": "李四",
  "email": "lisi@test.com",
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "expired_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 2
}

### 3. 创建租户 - 验证失败（缺少必填字段）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "缺少字段的租户"
}

### 4. 创建租户 - 验证失败（邮箱格式错误）
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenants
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD99",
  "name": "邮箱格式错误",
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "王五",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "phone": "13800138003",
  "expired_at": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 2
}

### ========================================
### 查询租户
### ========================================

### 5. 分页查询租户 - 默认参数
# @name listTenants
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants

### 6. 分页查询租户 - 带分页参数
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?page=1&page_size=10

### 7. 分页查询租户 - 按关键字搜索
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?keyword=测试

### 8. 分页查询租户 - 按状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?status=2

### 9. 分页查询租户 - 组合查询
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?page=1&page_size=5&keyword=科技&status=2

### ========================================
### 获取单个租户
### ========================================

### 10. 根据ID获取租户
# 使用上面创建的租户ID，需要手动替换
@tenantId = 019d7277075877c484deacd2d6af01bb
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}

### 11. 获取不存在的租户
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/01999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999

### ========================================
### 更新租户
### ========================================

### 12. 更新租户 - 部分字段
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "更新后的公司名称",
  "contact_name": "新联系人"
}

### 13. 更新租户 - 所有可更新字段
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000MA00ABCD13",
  "name": "完全更新公司",
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "新联系人",
  "email": "newemail@test.com",
  "phone": "13900139001",
  "expired_at": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "status": 1
}

### 14. 更新租户 - 邮箱格式错误
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "invalid-email-format"
}

### ========================================
### 删除租户
### ========================================

### 15. 删除租户
# 注意：删除后无法恢复
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenants/{{tenantId}}

### 16. 删除不存在的租户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenants/01999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999

### ========================================
### 健康检查
### ========================================

### 17. 存活检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/../health

### 18. 就绪检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/../ready
